Since my daughter Alecia gave me a Kiva gift card in 2009, I've helped fund 17 loans through Kiva.org — and 3 loans through Kiva Zip. I've also given 6 Kiva gift cards to family members and friends who, in turn, used my gift to fund 11 additional loans. Collectively, my Kiva impact helped fund 32 loans for individuals in 14 countries. *Whew!* 

I like to think that by participating as an individual lender through Kiva, I help people achieve their dreams and advance their missions …because it’s the right thing to do.
